com.evite.qv.webservice
Interface QVWebService

All Known Implementing Classes:
QVWebServiceImpl
public interface QVWebService

This is the interface of the evite web service gateway (for Quickvite, but generic enough to be reused). Legend: event - a thing/ocassion that happens, esp. of importance. host - this is person who organized/own the event. invitation - this is the object (in a form of card in real world) that you receive when someone invites you to an event. invitee - the person invited to the event.

Author:
jeff elo, allanlim, edgarjao
